网易新闻期间的前同事。 7 月下旬公布的中国教育 “双减” （中小学生减轻校内校外负担）政策，让所有从业者都不得不找新方向，不管这个方向是不是和教育相关。（晚点 LatePost）"},"attached_info":"Cj8I78Gtl8isrp1YEAMaCDcxOTA2MDYwIOaLuosGMCw42gxAAXIJNDkzMzExNjIzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"699 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-fe6ef272e03e35cd07e89dde4385fcf9_720w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1634792861.9900775","card_id":"Q_454756076","target":{"id":454756076,"title":"郭德纲在相声历史上是什么水平？如果现在退休，在相声史上是什么地位？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/454756076","type":"question","created":1618465898,"answer_count":245,"follower_count":459,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6134,6354,25687],"comment_count":26,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I78Gtl8isrp1YEAMaCDYzMzM2NzU1IOqo34MGMBo4ywNAAnIJNDU0NzU2MDc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"637 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-bbc9155208b30b7d14f4de81c7fa19d2_720w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1634792861.9904904","card_id":"Q_493626666","target":{"id":493626666,"title":"辽宁沈阳市一饭店发生燃气爆炸，已造成 3 人死亡、 30 余人受伤，目前情况如何？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/493626666","type":"question","created":1634779715,"answer_count":207,"follower_count":954,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3628,12503,16499,18618,20070],"comment_count":44,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"据辽宁省消防救援总队官方微博消息， 10 月 21 日 8 时 19 分，沈阳市消防救援支队指挥中心接到群众报警，位于和平区太原南街与南七马路交界处现场发生险情。指挥中心立即调派南京北街消防救援站、文化路消防救援站、腾飞二街消防救援站出动 25 辆消防车、 110 名消防指战员赶赴现场，同时全勤指挥部、西部指挥部及和平大队遂行出动。 经侦查，初步判定现场为商住楼楼内爆炸。市应急局、燃气公司、公安等部门已经到场处置。目前，救援正在进行中。 沈阳一饭店发生爆炸 已造成 3 人死亡、 30 余人受伤 据沈阳市和平区委宣